{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f6115d5f1c","title":"给田家英的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"0f332826a7","index":0,"year":1954,"month":3,"day":2,"articleId":"f6115d5f1c"}],"tags":[{"id":"2a70b5d939","name":"书信","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji34","name":"毛泽东全集第34卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/34-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji34":{"comments":[{"id":"eb0426928c","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"f6115d5f1c","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"杨秀生，杨开慧的族兄。"},{"id":"cb1c1dd15b","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"f6115d5f1c","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这里是以当时流通的人民币计算的，按中国人民银行1955年3月1日起发行的新人民币折算，合1200元（新币1元等于旧币1万元）。"},{"id":"19bc521514","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"f6115d5f1c","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"柳直商，曾任湖南省农民协会秘书长、中国工农红军第二军团政治部主任、中共鄂西分特委书记，1932年辆性。"}],"contents":[{"id":"e7c09bd731","type":"title","text":"给田家英的信","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"f6115d5f1c"},{"id":"eb0426928c","type":"paragraph","text":"家英同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"f6115d5f1c"},{"id":"cb1c1dd15b","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）杨秀生\"信请抄转长沙杨开智先生，询问信内所述情形是否属实，我完全不记得了。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"f6115d5f1c"},{"id":"19bc521514","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）今年寄杨家补助费1.200万元，上半年的600万元宜即寄去，请予办理。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"f6115d5f1c"},{"id":"1d0ccceb7f","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）李淑一女士，长沙柳直萄同志（烈士）的未亡人，教书为业，年长课繁，难乎为继。有人求我将她荐到北京文史馆为馆员，文史馆资格颜严，我荐了几人，没有录取，未便再荐。拟以我的稿费若干为助，解决这个问题，未知她本人愿意接受此种帮助否？她是杨开慧的亲密朋友，给以帮助也说得过去。请函询杨开智先生转询李淑一先生，请她表示意见。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"f6115d5f1c"},{"id":"6a29d34c65","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"f6115d5f1c"},{"id":"06978391fe","type":"paragraph","text":"三月二日","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"f6115d5f1c"}],"page":{"id":"3aac079440","publicationId":"maoquanji34","articleId":"f6115d5f1c","start":40,"end":40}}}},"__N_SSG":true}